Date: Wed, 11 Sep 2013 11:47:14 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] tools: add missing 'interface' type and update man page

https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1006699

Signed-off-by: Alex Jia <ajia@redhat.com>
(cherry picked from commit 4583ccbcf72d5cfb3f078d208c3efbf9aab0d799)
Signed-off-by: Jiri Denemark <jdenemar@redhat.com>
---
 tools/virt-xml-validate.in | 19 +++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 19 insertions(+)

diff --git a/tools/virt-xml-validate.in b/tools/virt-xml-validate.in
index 36bc6f2..1b61850 100644
--- a/tools/virt-xml-validate.in
+++ b/tools/virt-xml-validate.in
@@ -60,6 +60,9 @@ if [ -z "$TYPE" ]; then
      *secret*)
         TYPE="secret"
         ;;
+     *interface*)
+        TYPE="interface"
+        ;;
      *)
        echo "$0: cannot determine schema type for $XMLFILE"
        exit 3
@@ -100,6 +103,10 @@ Valid schema names currently include
 
 =over 4
 
+=item C<domainsnapshot>
+
+The schema for the XML format used by domain snapshot configuration
+
 =item C<domain>
 
 The schema for the XML format used by guest domains configuration
@@ -124,6 +131,18 @@ The schema for the XML format used by node device descriptions
 
 The schema for the XML format used to declare driver capabilities
 
+=item C<nwfilter>
+
+The schema for the XML format used by network traffic filters
+
+=item C<secret>
+
+The schema for the XML format used by secrets descriptions
+
+=item C<interface>
+
+The schema for the XML format used by physical host interfaces
+
 =back
 
